                <li class="mb-1"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-1"></i>Leadership (C)</li>
                <li class="mb-1"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-1"></i>Emotional Intelligence (D)</li>
                <li class="mb-1"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-1"></i>Performance (E)</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/register?userType=High+School" class="btn btn-warning btn-lg w-100">
